      "text": "# Conclusion"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "5790e10a00aaf26f",
      "text": "There are multiple ways to write in wiki. The current implementation has explored in depth the unique role of federation and forking in creating a new form of [[federated writing]] environment. "
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "153e3314f706ba68",
      "text": "It is time for this experiment to come full circle, federated wiki needs to incorporate the consensus writing capability of the original wiki, and this functionality can be added while retaining all the present benefits, and with only small additions to the code base."
